response.overview: Ever wonder what happens to a girl almost 10 years after making her debut in one of my tapes? Wonder no further, here's Amber Smith, who was in the first "Black Debutante" volume. She'd interesting all right! You'll see, Michelle Michael's first scene here with me. I'm still pinching myself! She's a hottie and will go far! Felix, on the cover, is a hottie too! This is her first scene too! I enjoyed working with Felix, Kendra makes her first appearance in a sex video too! She's into it as well. 4 very different girls, two common denominators.. You, the viewer and me. Not that we are common, of course, but what we do have in common is that we share them together!
response.title: More Dirty Debutantes 225
